Definition: a method of drying food or blood plasma or pharmaceuticals or tissue without destroying their physical structure
Example: material is frozen and then warmed in a vacuum so that the ice sublimes
Synonyms: lyophilization, verb, change, lyophilize, lyophilisation, lyophilise, freeze, dehydration, a, method, of, drying, food, or, blood, plasma, pharmaceuticals, tissue, without, destroying, their, physical, structure, material, is, frozen, and, then, warmed, in, vacuum, so, that, the, ice, sublimes
Category: noun.process
